  m_text: '<align="center">Farmer

    ----------------------------</align>

    Grow
    crops to attract wild creatures, and after they eat, there is a chance they become
    your companions.<br>A new seed will be unlocked every 5 level of the Agronomy
    stat.<br>Companions can be equipped to help the Warrior through the stages.<br><br>Extra
    befriended companions of the same species will be automatically converted into
    Bits.<br><br>Your companions may appear while farming and chill with you.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d84c0cc5ab8f8a048904ad938e7cf1aa, type: 2}
