  m_text: '<align="center">Fisher

    ----------------------------</align>

    Catch
    all fishes of a group to unlock a bonus.<br>Extra fishes will be automatically
    converted into Bits.<br>Different fishes can be found at different times of the
    day, like morning, afternoon, and evening.<br>Changing job will interrupt the
    current fishing session and reset the timer of the hook.'
